{"tid":2248452,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"白羅斯逾30萬民眾上街示威   要總統下台","createTime":"2020-10-18T15:04:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T15:42:31.000Z","uid":184679,"like":56,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"32ea190c200f74dddfab9c8e67d2ff5ccb2a9e5d","tid":2248452,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T15:04:49.000Z","msg":"白俄羅斯首都明斯克持續有示威，要求總統盧卡申科辭職。外電報道，當地星期日有逾30萬名民眾上街示威，無視警方高層日前表明不排除使用槍械對付示威者的警告。警方拘捕大約50人，市內部分地區流動數據網絡被中斷。 <br />\n<br />\n反對派早前向被指選舉舞弊的盧卡申科發出最後通牒，要求他在下星期日前宣佈辭職，否則發動全國罷工。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://stream.881903.com/public/d78c8fc4c0f48f4a6671b52eb155cc67/2020/10/12ffba585d8f4aeb88911a899751ef76.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstream.881903.com%2Fpublic%2Fd78c8fc4c0f48f4a6671b52eb155cc67%2F2020%2F10%2F12ffba585d8f4aeb88911a899751ef76.jpg&h=fd835878&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2362167\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2362167&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1a0cGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=8b78bd15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2362167</a>"},{"pid":"0a68bc9114447697469a14ffcc922f034a2aea38","tid":2248452,"uid":243677,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T15:09:11.000Z","msg":"白俄 泰國既同路人 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ff553d68ed44d951771e45322b83bd79773bd47","tid":2248452,"uid":276676,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0a68bc9114447697469a14ffcc922f034a2aea38","tid":2248452,"uid":243677,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T15:09:11.000Z","msg":"白俄 泰國既同路人 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"